{"tid":1069330,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"雙程漢菜刀喪劈打簿機變「斬崩刀」 便裝警擎槍繳械","createTime":"2019-03-20T01:43:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-20T04:29:17.000Z","uid":56881,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1dbdedfac1786a8856e074d5b56b751baeff5cfe","tid":1069330,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T01:43:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%9B%99%E7%A8%8B%E6%BC%A2%E8%8F%9C%E5%88%80%E5%96%AA%E5%8A%88%E6%89%93%E7%B0%BF%E6%A9%9F%E8%AE%8A%E3%80%8C%E6%96%AC%E5%B4%A9%E5%88%80%E3%80%8D-%E4%BE%BF%E8%A3%9D%E8%AD%A6%E6%93%8E%E6%A7%8D%E7%B9%B3-222247165.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%259B%2599%25E7%25A8%258B%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%258F%259C%25E5%2588%2580%25E5%2596%25AA%25E5%258A%2588%25E6%2589%2593%25E7%25B0%25BF%25E6%25A9%259F%25E8%25AE%258A%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%2596%25AC%25E5%25B4%25A9%25E5%2588%2580%25E3%2580%258D-%25E4%25BE%25BF%25E8%25A3%259D%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2593%258E%25E6%25A7%258D%25E7%25B9%25B3-222247165.html&d=0gDP8yh%2BwNUcUrQXLcOs9MkuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=040ea4f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%9B%99%E7%A8%8B%E6%BC%A2%E8%8F%9C%E5%88%80%E5%96%AA%E5%8A%88%E6%89%93%E7%B0%BF%E6%A9%9F%E8%AE%8A%E3%80%8C%E6%96%AC%E5%B4%A9%E5%88%80%E3%80%8D-%E4%BE%BF%E8%A3%9D%E8%AD%A6%E6%93%8E%E6%A7%8D%E7%B9%B3-222247165.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/dYaYM9jQpZfrvhkTYo9ZKA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/ae5743eeeebd604a61da10d12b2468f7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FdYaYM9jQpZfrvhkTYo9ZKA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2Fae5743eeeebd604a61da10d12b2468f7&h=16ebe891&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n紅磡發生一宗刀劈打簿機事件。(葉嘉文攝)<br />\n<br />\n上周末(16日)中午一名持刀漢揮刀斬傷超市經理，而被警員開槍擊斃，紅磡有持刀漢遭警員擎槍繳械。今日(20日)凌晨零時40分，西九龍衝鋒隊第3隊一輛警車巡經德民街16號時，<span style=\"color: red;\">發現一名男子，持菜刀闖入上址地下星展銀行24小時理財中心，向一部打簿機狂劈</span>。衝鋒隊一名便裝警員見狀落車，拔出伸縮警棍上前喝止，惟該男子未有就範，警員惟有拔出警槍戒備，男子見警槍即時被繳械「投降」。<br />\n<br />\n警方經調查後，不排除該男子精神混亂下犯案，將案件列刑事毀壞及藏有攻擊性武器，將姓邵涉案29歲男子拘捕，並由九龍城警區刑事調查隊接手跟進，警員檢走涉案菜刀，發現刀鋒呈現崩裂，懷疑邵破壞打簿機時，斬到「刀崩」。<br />\n<br />\n案中成功喝令疑犯棄刀投降的便裝警叫「阿榮」差齡7年，加入衝鋒隊約1年半，是次為首度擎槍制止暴力案件，他表示如對方持刀衝出理財中心，或會嚴重威脅途人性命，故當時覺得須以最快速度，將持有攻擊性武器的疑犯勸降或制服。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咪唔識用呀<br />\n定以為打簿機有錢出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1329d22925ddfebe6c872b2a4ffd1b7e27c0cff2","tid":1069330,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T01:46:23.000Z","msg":"打刧打簿機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b0ebebe74ecc667f87158ff07917a5917ff081e","tid":1069330,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T02:13:58.000Z","msg":"論教育嘅重要性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d52c39c4b908619cc439c8616fd7512458952e72","tid":1069330,"uid":98795,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T02:17:32.000Z","msg":"佢以為用把垃圾刀就可以嚇到條友出黎？<br />\n櫃員機話: 呀叔食過夜粥，唔瀉你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uCqHfUV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuCqHfUV.png&h=e2b923f5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"826b65f9fe9e82738c8211c875569de1646fece9","tid":1069330,"uid":5542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T02:17:46.000Z","msg":"幫佢印多幾個零？"},{"pid":"634f35c6f6356f12ac6648706c27655585235aba","tid":1069330,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T02:17:48.000Z","msg":"人蠢真係....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9f281258d39fd60894fc68151753c9da21d9